Introduction

At Kohinoor Gems & Jewellers, we create more than ornaments – we craft timeless stories of elegance, purity, and trust. Located in the heart of Udaipur, we blend traditional craftsmanship with contemporary designs.

– BIS Hallmarked Gold

– 925 Sterling Silver

– Certified Gemstones

– Custom Designs

– Heritage Jadav Work

– Premium Pearls

– Lifetime Trust

– Fair Pricing

About Us

At our jewellery house, we believe every ornament carries a story of love, tradition, and timeless beauty. With years of expertise, we craft pieces that blend heritage with contemporary elegance. From gold and silver to gemstones and pearls, our collection reflects purity and perfection. Each design is created with care, precision, and an eye for detail. We source only the finest materials, ensuring authenticity in every product. Our artisans bring life to traditional artistry with modern touches. Whether for daily wear or special occasions, we design jewellery that resonates with your style. Customer trust and satisfaction are the foundation of our brand. We aim to make luxury affordable without compromising on quality.

WORDS ABOUT US

Why Choose us

Because every jewel deserves trust, purity, and perfection.

At our jewellery house, we don’t just sell ornaments – we craft emotions, traditions, and memories that last forever. Every piece is designed with love, precision, and authenticity to give you an experience as precious as the jewel itself.

  • Unmatched Craftsmanship – Each jewel is created with intricate detailing, blending heritage artistry with modern elegance.
  • Authenticity Guaranteed – All gold and silver jewellery is BIS-hallmarked and certified for purity.
  • Exclusive Collections – From regal jadav sets to everyday silver wear, we offer designs you won’t find anywhere else.
  • Natural Gemstones & Pearls – Our gemstones, pearls, and rudraksh are handpicked for originality and healing value.
  • Tailored Creations – We specialize in custom-made jewellery that reflects your unique personality and style.
  • Trusted Legacy – With years of experience and thousands of happy customers, we are a name you can trust.
